text: John Gutch may refer to: *John Gutch (clergyman) (1746–1831), English Anglican clergyman and official of the University of Oxford *John Mathew Gutch (1776–1861), English journalist and historian *John Wheeley Gough Gutch (1809–1862), British surgeon and editor. *John Gutch (colonial administrator) (1905–1988), British colonial administrator who served as High Commissioner for the Western Pacific and Governor of the Solomon Islands
